---
title: Discover the Best Free Browser Games
description: Discover the best free browser games on ArcadeBloom. Browse action, puzzle, arcade and strategy games by category, read honest reviews, and play at the source.
permalink: /
---
{# Homepage — category portal style (ADR / CONTEXT.md "Homepage").
   Static pre-rendered: Hero + 6 category cards + Featured rail + New rail.
   No Recently Played, no JS-rendered rails. #}

{% extends 'base.njk' %}

{% set featured_games = games | featuredOnly | limit(8) %}
{% set new_games = games | sortByDateDesc | limit(8) %}
{% set total_games = games | length %}

{% block jsonld %}
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@graph": [
    {
      "@type": "WebSite",
      "name": "ArcadeBloom",
      "description": "{{ site.description }}",
      "url": "{{ site.url }}/",
      "publisher": { "@id": "{{ site.url }}/#org" },
      "potentialAction": {
        "@type": "SearchAction",
        "target": {
          "@type": "EntryPoint",
          "urlTemplate": "{{ site.url }}/search/?q={search_term_string}"
        },
        "query-input": "required name=search_term_string"
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "@id": "{{ site.url }}/#org",
      "name": "ArcadeBloom",
      "url": "{{ site.url }}/",
      "description": "A curated directory of free browser games.",
      "logo": "{{ site.url }}/og-image.png"
    }
  ]
}
</script>
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
{# Compact hero — brand + value prop + search. Tight (py-12) so the game grid
   lands in the first viewport, not after a wall of marketing copy. #}
<section class="hero-gradient py-10 lg:py-14">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight" style="text-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(10,16,45,0.45);">
                Discover the best free browser games.
            </h1>
            <p class="mt-4 text-base md:text-lg text-white/85 max-w-2xl">
                A curated directory of <strong>free online browser games</strong> — no download, no install.
                Read honest reviews, then play at the source. {{ total_games }} games catalogued and growing.
            </p>
            <form action="/search/" method="get" class="mt-5 flex gap-2 max-w-md">
                <input type="search" name="q" placeholder="Search {{ total_games }} games…"
                    class="flex-1 px-5 py-3 rounded-full border-0 bg-white/15 text-base focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white/60 placeholder-white/50">
                <button type="submit" class="primary-button">Search</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

{# === Editor's Picks — the first game grid, in-view right below the hero.
   This is the conversion target: user arrives → sees games → clicks one. === #}
{% set picks = featured_games | sortByScreenshotThenDate | limit(8) %}
{% if picks.length %}
<section class="py-10 lg:py-12">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="flex items-end justify-between mb-6">
            <div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold">Editor's Picks — jump straight in</h2>
                <p class="text-white/70 mt-1 text-sm md:text-base">Award-winning browser games, hand-picked. Click any card for the review and play link.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="/featured/" class="text-sm font-semibold text-sky-300 hover:text-white whitespace-nowrap">See all →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 md:gap-5">
            {% for game in picks %}
            {% include 'game-card.njk' %}
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    {% include 'ad-banner.njk' %}
</div>

<section class="py-10 lg:py-12">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold">Browse by Category</h2>
            <p class="text-white/70 mt-1 text-sm md:text-base">Six top-level categories covering every kind of browser game we catalogue.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 md:gap-6">
            {% for cat in site.categories %}
            {% set count = games | whereEq('category', cat.slug) | length %}
            {% set is_thin = count < site.minGamesPerCategory %}
            <a href="/category/{{ cat.slug }}/" class="glass-card p-5 hover:scale-[1.02] transition group {% if is_thin %}opacity-60{% endif %}">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                    <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold group-hover:text-white">{{ cat.name }}</h3>
                    <span class="badge">{{ count }}{% if is_thin %}<span class="ml-1 text-white/40">/ {{ site.minGamesPerCategory }}</span>{% endif %}</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-white/70 text-sm mt-2">{{ cat.blurb }}</p>
                {% if is_thin %}
                <p class="text-xs text-white/40 mt-2">Still seeding — browse what's here.</p>
                {% endif %}
            </a>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

{% if new_games.length %}
<section class="py-10 lg:py-12">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="flex items-end justify-between mb-6">
            <div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold">New Arrivals</h2>
                <p class="text-white/70 mt-1 text-sm md:text-base">The most recent additions to the directory.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="/new/" class="text-sm font-semibold text-sky-300 hover:text-white">See all →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 md:gap-5">
            {% for game in new_games %}
            {% include 'game-card.njk' %}
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

{# SEO content section — explains what the site is, reinforces topical relevance
   for "browser games / web games / free online games / game directory". #}
<section class="py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="glass-card p-8 sm:p-10 space-y-5">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">About ArcadeBloom — A Browser Game Directory</h2>
            <div class="text-white/75 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
                <p>
                    ArcadeBloom is a curated directory of <strong>free browser games</strong> — no downloads, no installs,
                    no walled garden. We catalogue the best <strong>web games</strong> from across the internet: open-source
                    projects on GitHub, indie titles on personal sites, and competition entries from events like js13kGames.
                    Every game in our directory links out to its original author's site, so you always play the real thing
                    where it lives.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Browse <a href="/category/puzzle/" class="text-sky-300 hover:text-white underline">puzzle games</a> for
                    logic and number challenges, <a href="/category/arcade/" class="text-sky-300 hover:text-white underline">arcade games</a>
                    for retro and score-attack fun, <a href="/category/action/" class="text-sky-300 hover:text-white underline">action games</a>
                    for reflex-driven shooters, or <a href="/category/strategy/" class="text-sky-300 hover:text-white underline">strategy games</a>
                    when you want to plan before you move. Each entry comes with an honest review, a how-to-play guide,
                    and transparent source attribution.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Unlike portals that re-host other people's work, ArcadeBloom is a <strong>game directory</strong>: we
                    discover, review, and link. That means cleaner licensing, fairer credit to creators, and a catalogue
                    you can trust. New <strong>free online games</strong> are added regularly — bookmark this page or
                    check the <a href="/new/" class="text-sky-300 hover:text-white underline">latest additions</a>.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
{% endblock %}
